+-_make_consequence(self, consequence_id: str, consequence_type: str, summary: str, event_type: str, payload: dict[str, Any], metadata: dict[str, Any] | None = None) -> ActionConsequence
+-Behavior by option type
+-investigate_thread
+-
+-Emit consequences like:
+-
+-thread_progressed
+-possibly scene_fact_established for a lead/clue placeholder if appropriate
+-do not invent hidden content yet; keep simple
+-talk_to_npc
